{"tid":1550678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Diu no english] 《香港人權與民主法案》簡單英文版","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:13:37.000Z","uid":210944,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4bf466db34e73c9ec042a6b29d46a87d86fc568","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"我知好多巴打都略略望過《香港人權與民主法案》嘅文<br />\n不過萬一真係有人用英文問都未必即刻答到<br />\n希望大家都可以larp一larp呢到 叫有個底<br />\n<br />\nsource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/十分鐘-了解-香港人權與民主法案/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%2F&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC4Bs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=c8158567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%2F&h=a7e80919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/十分鐘-了解-香港人權與民主法案/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/124402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F124402&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC4Bs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=4562c6af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/124402</a><br />\n<br />\nThe extradition bill proposed by the government threatened the autonomy and freedom in HK. This worries the US and rest of the world as it may harm their interests.<br />\n<br />\n港府強推《逃犯條例》修訂侵蝕香港的自由與自治，威脅到美國及其他國家在香港的利益<br />\n<br />\nHuman rights and democracy act aims to ensure and consolidate the autonomy of HK under the supervision of US, and thus help us to rebuild international confidence.<br />\n<br />\n《香港人權與民主法案》強化美國對香港自治狀況的支持和監察，同時亦會加強國際社會對香港的信心<br />\n<br />\nHow it works: Under the act, US congress will review the level of autonomy of HK every year and decide whether to continue providing preferential treatments to HK base on that. Moreover, it gives the US president the power to blacklist those who harm or help to damage the human rights condition/ democracy/ autonomy in HK, froze their assets in US and ban them from entering the boarder of the states of freedom.<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿每年需向國會提交報告，查證香港有足夠自治權，才能延續中港區別的待遇。<br />\n同時，《香港人權與民主法案》賦予美國總統權力，可將侵害香港人權、民主和自治者列入黑名單，禁止入境及凍結其在美資產。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點:<br />\n不斷提ensure HK&rsquo;s autonomy就實冇死!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n早啲瞓 聽日遮打約定你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb214cac05b94095decd6c80632ff4a1c49ed168","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e851febff0d105e7520e737189decd8d2a83d9c7","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"808ef40509cfa92c43d82366a3afc527d72974c8","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9c160972eecf5a953890a1ac3eadfa947c6d227c","tid":1550678,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faefe64fc5bcb0b121d7611997336f5cf2463e87","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3d7b1c2d27fa890fdb06109460833bc176663010","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"33d5dfa87b1c3ee46fdb420e51239e4eaf48046e","tid":1550678,"uid":156145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"出！！"},{"pid":"044347a4dddd518dcf3664681e731edc5b663f1b","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b060441fcedebdb59f70e9de89deb7be12352bf9","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"2adb2389fbe841716a96e9fcc3d1c5246073d092","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9daa67b08caf4e5bcefd8c7ca3a4fe7d73a46c6b","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"10441cfad0cec7a41f8ff6281e2e16c46cc6aefe","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"9162ad857b220842b8d1744d79c088fe5df7a430","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"aa50e86e516a50585dc8e160d65cae69c3eead66","tid":1550678,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"5a3a8ea2355286a9f7aa98be8d4